description: Welcome to Unit 402 at The Ellery! Prepare to be wowed with an 180-degree of Boston from the moment you step into this home. At almost 1100 sq ft, the wide plank oak flooring and Calcutta quartz counters exude elegance, while the oversized cabinets and custom closets offer ample storage. With in-unit laundry, surround sound, GE Cafe appliances, wine fridge, and more, no corner was cut. Right around the block from the Red Line, this home is transit-oriented and located close to major highways, offering easy access to the city and beyond. And, you'll enjoy an expansive common terrace and kitchenette to host friends all summer. Situated in a A+ location, this property is ripe for appreciation, making it an excellent investment opportunity. Whether you're a savvy investor or a discerning homeowner, this home is ready to fulfill your urban living dreams. This is 44 Ellery.
